    "description": "Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions is actively seeking a talented and motivated Consultant Physician to join our dynamic team in Navi Mumbai. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions:\nSolara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions!",
